-- Toyota Halts Production in India After Nationwide Worker Strike, NHK Says
-- Tak Kumakura
-- 2010-07-05T22:48:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-05/toyota-halts-production-in-india-after-nationwide-worker-strike-nhk-says.html

          
          
             Toyota Motor Corp. yesterday halted
all its production in India because of a nationwide worker
strike, Japanese broadcaster NHK reported, without saying where
it obtained the information. The company plans to resume
production today, the report said.  
          
          


  


        